    91	/// The fix preserves nullability by checking isNullableRefType().
    92	///
    93	/// This test exercises the externalized reference code path in ref.test via
    94	/// the extern.convert_any + ref.test pattern, verifying correct behavior for
    95	/// both nullable and non-nullable ref.test targets, as well as null and
    96	/// non-null input values.
    97	TEST(ExecutorRegression, RefTestNullAbility) {
    98	  WasmEdge::Configure Conf;
    99	  WasmEdge::VM::VM VM(Conf);
